{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "b3f2a6b0-1c2d-4e3f-9a8b-7c6d5e4f3a2b",
    "name": "SimplePSP - Demo Payment Gateway",
    "description": "Exercises the SimplePSP demo gateway end to end: the signed REST API (direct + hosted flows, capture/refund/void, idempotency), the merchant portal, the operator admin area, the shop, and the mock acquirer.\n\n**Before running:**\n1. `pnpm dev` (starts shop:4100, gateway:4101, acquirer:4102, portal:4103)\n2. `pnpm db:migrate && pnpm db:seed` - prints the operator password and demo merchant credentials (`pk_demo` / `sk_demo_secret` are fixed, the operator password is random each seed run)\n3. Paste the printed operator password into the `operatorPassword` collection variable before using the Admin folder.\n\nThe **Gateway API** folder auto-signs every request with HMAC-SHA256 via a folder-level pre-request script, exactly like `packages/shared/src/hmac.ts` - no manual header work needed. The **Portal** and **Admin** folders rely on Postman's cookie jar for the sealed-cookie session set by login.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "gatewayUrl", "value": "http://localhost:4101", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "shopUrl", "value": "http://localhost:4100", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "acquirerUrl", "value": "http://localhost:4102", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "portalUrl", "value": "http://localhost:4103", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "apiKey", "value": "pk_demo", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "apiSecret", "value": "sk_demo_secret", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "paymentId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "merchantId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "idempotencyKey", "value": "demo-idem-key-1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "merchantEmail", "value": "merchant@demo.test", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "merchantPassword", "value": "demo_password", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "operatorEmail", "value": "admin@demo.test", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "operatorPassword", "value": "REPLACE_WITH_PRINTED_SEED_PASSWORD", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "newMerchantId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
